# Kalite Kapıları

## Test Coverage

| Alan | Line | Branch |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Kritik modüller (authz, workflow, document, audit, crypto, notification) | ≥%90 | ≥%85 |
| Backend toplam | ≥%80 | ≥%70 |
| Frontend kritik form/guard/hook | ≥%70 | — |

Her auth/workflow/document testinde **en az bir negatif deny** senaryosu zorunlu.

## CI Pipeline (PR Zorunlu)

Install → lint → typecheck → unit → integration → SAST → SCA → secret scan → build → container scan. Hepsi green olmadan merge yok.

Security-sensitive dosya değişikliği → ek reviewer (Bilgi Güvenliği veya kıdemli dev).

## TypeScript

- `strict: true`, `noImplicitAny: true`, `strictNullChecks: true`
- `any`, `@ts-ignore`, `as any` → review red
- Shared DTO: `packages/dto` Zod schema — FE/BE duplicate schema yasak

## Frontend Kalite

- Lighthouse (Faz 11+): performance ≥80, a11y ≥90
- Bundle initial < 200 KB gzipped
- `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` yasak · `localStorage` yasak (session cookie-only)
- Web Vitals: LCP < 2.5s, CLS < 0.1

## API Performans Hedefleri

- İç ekranlar p95 < 500 ms
- Dış form submit p95 < 2 s

## OWASP ASVS

MVP'de L3 kritik %80; kalan %20 production öncesi. HIGH/CRITICAL bulgu ile release yok.

